     misc_feature    1..407
                     /label=FULL terminator rgn matching MG1655 CP032667.1
                     /note="""RIBOSOMAL RNA TERMINATOR REGION"": all matches E 
                     coli MG1655 CP032667.1 from BLAST-nt (4351105 to 4351511)
                     sequence upstream of this DOES NOT match the E. coli 
                     reference anymore, so this is true 5' end of ""terminator 
                     region"".
                     This sequence corresponds to last 7 nts of 23S ribosomal 
                     RNA-coding sequence + a gap + rrf (5S ribosomal RNA-coding 
                     sequence) + downstream sequence containing terminators for 
                     presumably both of these rRNA genes (seems like they are 
                     transcribed in tandem, though perhaps there is an 
                     additional terminator between the two not annotated here).
                     "
